                      <font face="arial" size="2" color="#000000"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> Heh,<br /><br />While looking for Seduction of Saryn I noticed Child of Bertox for 15k, so I bought it with a What the hell, why the hell not mentality.<br /><br />Got Seduction of Saryn a couple days later for 13k, and Word of Terris for 10k... But anyways.<br /><br />Child of Bertox was a complete waste of 15k, not only does it do less, or very slighty more damage than the 61 LoZ pet, its HP doesnt seem to make a difference, nor does the DS. Which makes me come to think it either has BUGGED damage, BUGGED mitigation, or BUGGED HP/AC. <br /><br />I spend about an hour in the arena with a friend, Rune of Death on each pet, and let CoB cast its Damage Shield... LoZ vs. CoB, each fight CoB won with around 5-15% life left, and 2 of the fights LoZ acctually won!. I have logs to prove it. This was without any interferance from either necromancer, or any other players.<br /><br />As for mobs... I dont really notice a difference besides a couple seconds getaway time for when I fuck up in PoP or otherwise.<br /><br /><br />I'll think of more to come....</span id="msg"></font>
